description.en:
What is the project about? Evany is a utility token that can replace the traditional payment method. Use Evany everywhere, anytime.


What makes your project unique? Our vision at Evany is to become a leading utility token within the GPoint Wallet ecosystem and beyond. We envision a future where our users can transact with Evany seamlessly and securely.


History of your project. Evany has been launched for trade on Lbank Exchange on April 20, 2023.


What’s next for your project? Evany will start on completing the road map and more exchanges to list. (


What can your token be used for? Evany can be used in GPoint Wallet (https://gpointwallet.com/), its main part of eco system.
